column4:
This fixed telephony support, maintenance and modernisation procurement (“Fixed Telephony Procurement”) is required to procure a service provider to deliver i) telephony modernisation services and ii) support and related services in regard to operational elements of TfL’s fixed telephony system (Fixed Telephony). There are three key components to the Fixed Telephony Procurement: 
• modernise TfL’s current Fixed Telephony system and estate (“Modernisation Services”);  
• provide on-going support and maintenance of the fixed telephony estate (“Support Services”); 
• future, additional catalogues services and projects, such as further upgrade projects (Additional Services).

